text: The manager seemed to be the only employee at the register and in the kitchen... Having had worked in a chain restaurant before I understand his plight. However, it is no excuse for poor customer service. My mother, who is a diabetic asked …More

name: Sonny Del Monte
text: It was exactly what I expected. Is it the best pizza, no it's not. But is it over all good? Yes it is. The staff was very friendly.

name: My First My Last
text: Had to leave without ordering anything because the manager's service was horrible.  He had let other customers cut in front of us in line and take their order. He did not ask us while we was waiting to order.

name: Richard Diamond
text: No longer a fan. They used to be on top, but... New national recipe, or new chef, my pizza was too salty. Also, counter man let me order 3 slices when a small pie was cheaper. Fair? Nope.

name: Will Smith
text: Dog food of the Pizza world. I used to enjoy Papa Gino's pizza but this was bad. Poor delivery driver attitude, forgot part of the order. Manager offered to drive another cookie out, really? Just take it off the bill. Not an option. Waste of money and time.
